{"tid":2197824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"車cam拍下差館外兜圈　 白衣漢涉舉鋤頭衝人群　警車駛經無停低","createTime":"2020-09-11T01:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T03:35:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0102151cfe3b3fbb0cfe6842295568bec425c4e7","tid":2197824,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/TXCORUW3HFHYXNUFCIR7NF7UNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FTXCORUW3HFHYXNUFCIR7NF7UNI%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=252d4ce3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FTXCORUW3HFHYXNUFCIR7NF7UNI%2F&h=df2bc3b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/TXCORUW3HFHYXNUFCIR7NF7UNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n車cam拍下差館外兜圈 <br />\n白衣漢涉舉鋤頭衝人群 警車駛經無停低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月5日「大三罷」，旺角有群眾聚集。其間一名六旬退休漢聲稱深夜遭示威者包圍，疑拾起鐵鋤自衞，並在街頭遊走，被控一項公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪受審。目擊證人稱一名白衫白褲男曾在旺角警署外舉起鐵鋤，近距離指向黑衣少年，並手持鐵鋤衝向人群，導致路人慌忙走避。證人的行車記錄儀拍下曾有警車駛經鐵鋤男身旁，但沒有停車。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨在西九。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rbI_KTg4-ei9pqBWhB_WPnPedjE=/996x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3JZQVVLSINFUHDPFZUZGVO7B3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrbI_KTg4-ei9pqBWhB_WPnPedjE%3D%2F996x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3JZQVVLSINFUHDPFZUZGVO7B3E.jpg&h=bf2f20a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告朱木源昨日就一項公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪受審。<br />\n<br />\n拘捕被告的警員陳俊源稱，當晚凌晨2時半巡至水渠道時，市民報稱附近有白衣男手持鋤頭並指出涉案的被告，他遂截停被告查問。被告自言駕車途經西洋菜南街欲下車買煙，突然有一班人衝向他並作狀施襲。他感害怕，遂隨手拾起路上的鋤頭自衞，「冇拎過出嚟攻擊任何人」。<br />\n<br />\n當晚駕車途經現場姓舒的飛機。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n白衣男及後在警署外高舉鐵鋤，鋤頭指向一名黑衣少年，兩者相距僅一至兩呎，白衣男及後將鋤頭「一下鋤咗落地」，少年慌忙跑離。其後，該白衣男衝向一堆聚集人群並舉起鋤頭，人群再次慌忙走避。舒最終在通菜街重遇白衣男，即向附近警員報案，指「有人管有攻擊性武器」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BdrINCZvagvU9L701EvPBWz_nUo=/1186x889/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/54J4RGGUU5BVPO54MSE3L2TQBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBdrINCZvagvU9L701EvPBWz_nUo%3D%2F1186x889%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F54J4RGGUU5BVPO54MSE3L2TQBQ.jpg&h=db6c4947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■從證人車cam片段可見，一名白衫白褲男子拖行鐵鋤頭（箭嘴示）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S0EtzMPldmmPHeen3vdpg9jNON0=/716x537/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/627SOFDM7NAKXPIJI6OIBYSQO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS0EtzMPldmmPHeen3vdpg9jNON0%3D%2F716x537%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F627SOFDM7NAKXPIJI6OIBYSQO4.jpg&h=79a53038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警署外有警車行經白衣男子（箭嘴示）旁，但沒有停車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證人：警稱受傷才構成攻擊<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問舒，指他向警方錄取的口供並無提及企圖攻擊或驚慌走避等字眼，質。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指車cam拍不到白衣男將鋤頭鋤向地，而事實上黑衣少年當時步伐正常沒奔跑；舒強調白衣男確有鋤地，因角度問題拍不到，但同意少年沒奔跑。<br />\n<br />\n郭棟明盤問舒時，雙方多次就字眼和表達方式爭議。舒透露中四便赴美升學。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC1411/20"},{"pid":"956379e190c565ed89b462ce5b8b784b989ff973","tid":2197824,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81c62ceee2df17cc109ff91488d7a9a2b7843330","tid":2197824,"uid":96871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"白衫人又贏"},{"pid":"e1e4218344914d70856a46eac109a88b30a38173","tid":2197824,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji